headline: Dollar Tree Q4 Earnings on Deck: What Surprise Awaits Investors?
summary: DLTR has been witnessing higher selling, general and administrative expenses for a while now. This, along with soft demand for discretionary items, is likely to weigh on fourth-quarter fiscal 2024 results.
